column5: We headed out to the island on sat to try our luck in the rain. Got a few each but could only get a couple pics due to the rain. all fish were caught on counterstrikes and proteges on a med to fast retrieve.  Here are a few pics,
nice work.cant wait to get a crack at some gators
Great stuff Ryan ! Will be trying the same baits out in a couple weeks and see what we swirl up ! Unfortunate that I have to wait 'till the 3rd Saturday for Pike now.. but so be it !
Hey, some nice pics of some nice pike.  Thanks for that report.  Gotta love that urban fishing!
Nice stuff guys.  Nice to see the island pike reports return!
Great Report! Looks like we are in for another great season!
